<p>It also has a higher concurrent peak than <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/apex-legends">Apex Legends</a>, Marvel Rivals, and <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/destiny-2">Destiny 2</a>.</p>
<p>Of course, we already knew that <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/battlefield-6-dominates-steam-charts-ahead-of-worldwide-release-as-analyst-estimates-over-100m-in-pre-launch-sales">Battlefield 6 was dominating Steam</a> as the top-selling game on the platform. One analyst has estimated it's already made over $100m in pre-launch sales before it's even out. And the shooter's not even just garnering high numbers, but it's getting high praise, too; at the time of writing, <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2807960/Battlefield_6/#app_reviews_hash">78 percent of the 25,000+ user Steam reviews are positive</a>.</p>
